00:01:17.154 --> 00:01:22.554
kicked, he would either go “ow”, or there would be a hollow thud.

00:01:23.814 --> 00:01:30.104
See, one of his legs was plastic, it was amputated below the knee, he had a prosthetic leg.

00:01:31.594 --> 00:01:35.424
We knew that he had fought in the Second World War, so in our little

00:01:35.434 --> 00:01:39.884
boy's imagination, this was some kind of glorious battle wound.

